author: USA TODAY, Jeanine Santucci, USA TODAY
title: 'This is ridiculous': Wisconsin voters had some strong words for their leaders while waiting to vote
description: Many voters called out state leaders over the decision to go forward with in-person voting. Wisconsin has more than 2,500 cases of coronavirus.
content:
